{
  "_doc": "Machine-readable metadata for the '{{skill_name}}' {{kind}}. Produced by skill-generator. Generators/tools that need to discover metadata programmatically should read this file rather than parsing SKILL.md. This file is self-contained: it does not require reading any other asset to be understood.",
